HEADWORD: Pigwidgeon
<hw>Pig"wid`geon</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Written also
<ets>pigwidgin</ets> and <ets>pigwiggen</ets>.]</ety> <def>A cant word
for anything petty or small. It is used by Drayton as the name of a
fairy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

